<p class="blue_title">&nbsp;</p>

<h2><strong><a name="order_arrive"></a>When will my order arrive?</strong></h2>
<p>The amount of time it takes your order to arrive at your  home or post office box depends on the shipping method you choose. Please visit  our <a href="shipping.html">Shipping Information</a> page for more information on estimated  arrival times.</p>
<p align="right"><span class="note"><a href="#top"><br>
</a></span><a href="#top">Back to top<br>
</a></p>
<h2><strong><a name="successfully_processed"></a>How  can I tell if my order was successfully processed?</strong></h2>
<p>After you enter your credit card information and click  &ldquo;Submit Order,&rdquo; a window will display the order number and the list of items  ordered. An order receipt will be sent to the email address you provided with your  billing information.</p>
<p align="right"><span class="note"><a href="#top"><br>
  </a></span><a href="#top">Back to top
  </a></p>
<h2><strong><a name="order_ship"></a>When  will my order ship?</strong></h2>
<p>Orders are usually shipped from our distribution facility  within one to two business days of the date the order was placed.</p>
<p align="right"><span class="note"><a href="#top"><br>
</a></span><a href="#top">Back to top</a></p>
<h2><strong><a name="my_order"></a>How  can I track my order?</strong></h2>
<p>If you chose one of the UPS shipping options, a tracking  number is supplied in the Shipment Confirmation email you were sent. You can  use this number at UPS.com to track your order status. This option is not  available for orders shipping through the United States Postal Service (USPS).</p>
<p align="right"><a href="#top">Back to top</a>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><strong><a name="change_it"></a>There is an error in my address on the order I just placed.  Can I change it?</strong></h2>
<p>  Because orders are processed at our distribution facility  within 24 hours of order placement, it is not always possible to make an  address change. If you need to change the address on your order, please email  us as soon as possible at
  <script language=javascript><!--
	  var name = "cpshop"
	  var site = "clubpenguin.com"
	  var link = name + "@" + site
	  document.write("<b><a href=" + "mail" + "to:" + link + ">" + link + "</a></b>")
	  //--></script>.</p>
<p align="right"><a href="#top">Back to top</a>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><a name="been_placed"></a>Can I make a change to my order after it has been placed?</h2>
<p>Order changes are possible but not guaranteed. The Club  Penguin Shop must be contacted within 24 hours from when the order was placed  to make any changes. Send your request to 
  <script language=javascript><!--
	  var name = "cpshop"
	  var site = "clubpenguin.com"
	  var link = name + "@" + site
	  document.write("<b><a href=" + "mail" + "to:" + link + ">" + link + "</a></b>")
	  //--></script> 
  While we  will do our best to meet your request, we cannot guarantee it. All changes must  be intercepted before distribution processing has occurred.</p>
<p align="right"><a href="#top">Back to top</a>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><strong><a name="exchange_it"></a>An item in my order is defective/doesn&rsquo;t fit. How do I  exchange it?</strong></h2>
<p>  We would be happy to replace an item in your order if it is  defective or doesn&rsquo;t fit. Please see our <a href="index.html">Customer Service</a> page  to find out how you can get an exchange or a refund.</p>
<p align="right"><a href="#top">Back to top</a>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><strong><a name="to_order"></a>How do I know what size clothing item to order?</strong></h2>

  Each clothing item has a product page with a link to its  corresponding sizing information. Please read it over carefully before making  your purchase. If you are still unsure after reading the sizing information,  compare the dimensions of a shirt you own that fits well to the dimensions  given for the shirt you want to purchase from our shop. Our dimensions show the  width measured under the armpit, and the length measured down the center of the  back.
  <p align="right"><a href="#top">Back to top</a>&nbsp;</p>
  
  <h2><strong><a name="Credit_Card"></a>Can I pay for an order without a Credit Card?</strong></h2>
  <p>    Currently, you can use Visa and MasterCard to pay for your  Club Penguin merchandise. We plan to add PayPal as another option in mid-2007.  We do not accept cash, checks, or money orders at this time.</p>
  <p align="right"><a href="#top">Back to top</a>&nbsp;</p>  
  <h2><strong><a name="US_Dollars"></a>Can I pay with a currency other than US Dollars?</strong></h2>
  <p>  The Club Penguin Shop accepts all forms of currency that can  be paid through Visa or MasterCard. All currencies are automatically converted  to US funds by our payment processing company.</p>
  <p align="right"><a href="#top">Back to top</a>&nbsp;</p>
  <h2><strong><a name="certain_date"></a>When should I place an order to receive it by a certain  date?</strong></h2>
  <p>    If you need to receive your order by a certain date, we  strongly recommend you read over the available shipping methods and estimated  delivery times on our <a href="shipping.html">Shipping Information</a> page.</p>
  <p><em><br>
    If  you did not see your question answered here, please send us an email at: 
  
